Package io.github.kale_ko.bjsl

Class BJSL<T extends Parser>

java.lang.Object
io.github.kale_ko.bjsl.BJSL<T>
Type Parameters:
T - The parser to use
public class BJSL<T extends Parser> extends Object
The main class for interfacing with BJSL

Static calls use default instances of each parser and processor

Since:
1.1.0
Version:
2.0.0
